{% from "components/emoji/macro.njk" import emoji %}

<h2>Meaningful emoji (default)</h2>
<p>
  Emergency services:
  {{ emoji({ text: "🚑", label: "Ambulance" }) }}
  {{ emoji({ text: "🚒", label: "Fire engine" }) }}
  {{ emoji({ text: "🚓", label: "Police car" }) }}
</p>

<h2>Decorative emoji (adjacent to duplicate text)</h2>
<p>
  Call NHS 111 {{ emoji({ text: "📞", decorative: true }) }} for non-emergency advice.
</p>
<p>
  Email the clinic {{ emoji({ text: "✉️", decorative: true }) }} at help@example.com.
</p>
